        public Omssahit(ResultSet aRS)
         throws SQLException
        This constructor reads the spectrum file from a resultset. The ResultSet should be positioned such that a single row can be read directly (i.e., without calling the 'next()' method on the ResultSet).
        Parameters:
        aRS - ResultSet to read the data from.
        Throws:
        SQLException - when reading the ResultSet failed.
